}}   '''Video DownloadHelper'''是[[Firefox瀏覽器|Firefox瀏覽器]]和[[Google_Chrome|Google Chrome]]的一个[[附加组件_(Mozilla)|扩展]] 。它允许用户从通過[[HTTP协议|HTTP协议]]传输视频的网站下载视频<ref>{{Cite web|title=Buffering Too Slow? Watch Videos When They're Complete With Video DownloadHelper|url=https://www.pcworld.com/article/249076/video_downloadhelper.html|accessdate=|author=PC World|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413083408/https://www.pcworld.com/article/249076/video_downloadhelper.html}}</ref>。该扩展由法國人米歇尔·古铁雷斯（Michel Gutierrez）开发，自2008年起登陸Firefox<ref>{{Cite web|title=This One Man Startup's App Has 85 Million Downloads And Is Wildly Profitable|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/firefox-video-downloadhelper-2011-3|accessdate=|author=business insider|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2014-05-22|archive-url=https://archive.is/20140522040722/www.businessinsider.com/firefox-video-downloadhelper-2011-3}}</ref>。截至2019年12月，Video DownloadHelper是Firefox第三大最受欢迎的扩展（仅次于[[Adblock_Plus|Adblock Plus]]和[[UBlock_Origin|UBlock Origin]]）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Popular extensions – Add-ons for Firefox|url=https://addons.mozilla.org/search/?sort=users&type=extension|accessdate=6 December 2019|publisher=Mozilla}}</ref>。

